reFrag: is an annual symposium exploring new connections between art, culture and technology. reFrag: Glitch presents the different ways that digital anomalies artistically manifest themselves in our daily life. The alterations are produced in different domains: deconstruction of instabilities and errors of the financial markets, hacking and tactical anomalies and the absence of neutrality in technological systems.
