A selection of international artists reveals the unseen aspects in any technological innovation, by
underlining its temporary, playful, enslaving or threatening dimensions when urging in the same time
to alternative or subversive uses. Aside from the exhibition, the festival took form in performances, talks, conferences, workshops, concerts etc.
